Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们真的要过上没有后辈的高中生活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得那样也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:31.24,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,900)\pos(271,601)} #8     「想做的事是」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之在校园观摩上开演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能通过这样来增加新生数量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后学生会采取独立行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想方设法阻止废校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要说的说出来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这次协商讨论的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样做才能增加新生的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就多介绍点有意思的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学校历史和师资力量也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得以往的学生会有点太死板了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说这里的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不少人都说很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不错  来把这种优点展现出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园偶像很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦  我们学校也有  是缪斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托她们开一场演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  意外地很受外校学生欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是学园偶像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  接下来有校园观摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话希望你们来开场演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还什么都没有决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  大家都很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  这下能赶得上校园观摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的能开演唱会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被学生会长阻止的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那点没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有介绍社团的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那时候唱歌的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节奏还没对上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  再练习一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们终于追上仁子的等级了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没办法比现在更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底对什么不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法让人感动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就凭现在这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  海未说要去学舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  看了她的芭蕾后我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的舞蹈还远远不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说有事  就这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是学生会长对我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌吧  绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嫉妒吧  嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解一个那么擅长跳舞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了我们的表演后说我们是外行的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反对  说不定会被她毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  高三生有我仁子一个就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长  有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  身边有个舞蹈很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要跳得更好的话就得去请教她没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的话  我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着拜托一下她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点想看绘里学姐的舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那明天去问她一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成什么样我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  历史悠久的音木坂学院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直促进着本地的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  当时的学院还被称为音乐学院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院内有很多以艺术家为目标的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着创造性十足的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这所音木坂学院里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体重增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半段非常吸引我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在校园观摩那天前修正的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  随便说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么姐姐要说这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想废校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不希望音木坂消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是姐姐想做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会讨厌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的学校要是被废校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你为了阻止废校过分勉强自己了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘里真固执
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让学校延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我教你们舞蹈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  能教我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想跳得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想被你说得那么差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不能赞同你们的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可否认你们很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要做就要请你们努力达到我的标准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星辰开始移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVELIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚濑同学  很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意这种选拔会的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你们能走到今天这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还好好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们因为基础没有打好所以才会洋相百出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腿打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  保持腿部张开的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要让腹部碰到地板才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高柔软性关系到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要让你们全员能做到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话正式演出会很悬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的预感  命中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是佩服的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠舞蹈把人迷住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这种事也是理所应当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肌肉训练重新再练一次比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后再来一组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用那样说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是进行了冷静的判断而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们多少也应该知道自己的实力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的校园观摩关系到学校的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们做不到就早说吧  别浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里沙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  看着缪斯的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里就会感受到一阵暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拼命努力  又非常享受的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比起姐姐是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我非常受到她们的鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在偷看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先做柔软体操是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天做了那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又要做同样的事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根本就不知道能不能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们想去做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然练习的确很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身酸疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想要阻止废校的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不会输给学生会长的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  今天也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是姐姐想做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们想去做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  看着缪斯的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里就会感受到一阵暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拼命努力  又非常享受的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了绘里的朋友  又在学生会工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在想一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘里真正想做的事情究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直在一起  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘里总是为了别人在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看起来好像一直在忍耐着什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有考虑自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要让学校保留下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为学生会长的义务感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以理事长才没有赞成你的行动不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘里的  绘里真正想做的事情是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要想点办法  这也是没办法的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想只做自己喜欢的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样就能解决问题的话我也想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己很笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还说得出「我们来做偶像吧」这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长  不  绘里学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习？那么先把昨天布置的课题全部完成…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘里学姐  请加入缪斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起在缪斯作为校园偶像一起歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么  我怎么可能会做那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我听希学姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的话就老实点说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁子学姐可没资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说想做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  我来当偶像什么的  很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要什么特别的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做就做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正想做的事情  都是那样开始的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘里学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就8个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是9个人  加上我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希学姐也来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我占卜的结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个组合达到9人的时候  未来之门就会打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会取名为  9位歌唱的女神  缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那么取了那个名字的……原来是希学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是音木坂学院的校园偶像  缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很喜欢这个音木坂学院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有这个学校  才会有成员们的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会集齐这9个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要表演的歌曲  是我们凑齐9人以后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一首作好的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的起步之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我们的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:32.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(640,650)}僕らのLIVE  君とのLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的LIVE  与你共度的LIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:06.78,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな今よりも新しい夢つかまえたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:06.78,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比起一成不变的现今  去追求新的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:14.58,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大胆に飛び出せば  O.K.マイライフ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:14.58,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大胆地飞奔出去就行了  O.K. MYLIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.01,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}望みは大きくね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.01,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愿望要越大越好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:25.12,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}背のびだってば  高く遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:25.12,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}探起身子  遥望远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:30.27,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まぶしいあした抱きしめに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:30.27,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀抱着闪耀的明天前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:34.24,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部叶えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:34.24,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部都要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:38.63,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうだよ  信じるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:38.63,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}没错  只要你坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:45.97,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ぐんぐん前に進むよ、君が！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:45.97,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就能勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:50.90,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}答えなくていいんだわかるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:50.90,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使你不回答我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:55.06,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸にえがく場所は同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:55.06,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在胸中描绘的场景是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:21:04.77,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何度でも諦めずに  探すことが僕らの挑戦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:21:04.77,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论如何都不放弃  不断探求是我们的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:09.13,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}元気の温度は下がらない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:09.13,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}元气的温度不会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:13.28,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱いままで羽ばたいてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:13.28,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀抱着热情振翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:18.28,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あこがれを語る君の
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:18.28,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}诉说着憧憬的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:29.34,INlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,700)}ゆずらない瞳がだいすき…ダイスキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:29.34,INlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,700)}那双坚定的眼神让我倾心…让我倾心！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.61,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直に追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.61,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}坦率地去追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.53,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気で追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.53,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}充满勇气地去追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:28.08,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さな願いが明日を作る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:28.08,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的愿望化为了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:34.21,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}できるかも　みんなが望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:34.21,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要大家期望  那就能够做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:37.17,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰より頑張っちゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:37.17,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比谁都要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.26,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とにかく情熱のままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.26,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣满腔的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:46.47,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目指すのは綺麗な風吹く道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:46.47,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}以那凉风习习的大道为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:52.77,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}羽のように　腕上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:52.77,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}像展翅一般抬起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:58.44,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まぶしい未来へと　飛ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:58.44,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飞向那灿烂的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:02.57,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きっと青春が聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:02.57,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定能够聆听到青春的音符
